    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唐三藏只是一介凡人，没有通天的手段，他要怎么在凶险万分的妖魔世界中闯出生天？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293850/extras/d7ddb794e2a8ab1d7abce9ad0912054c.poster.avif?t=1737034417\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293850/extras/d7ddb794e2a8ab1d7abce9ad0912054c.webm?t=1737034417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293850/extras/d7ddb794e2a8ab1d7abce9ad0912054c.mp4?t=1737034417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏以唐三藏的主角，为了解放孙悟空而借用金箍棒攀爬五指山，途中将会遇到各种逆天的难关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为唐三藏，理解唐三藏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提示：如果卡关，多跟悟空交互以寻求帮助。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特性</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用可伸缩的金箍棒攀爬悬崖峭壁。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小小的失误，就会让你掉回谷底！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >避开雷云.……否则会被轰飞！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接受孙悟空疯狂的嘲笑！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很难过？那就哭吧。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293850/extras/1d6d06c9adf669985008213852a18310.poster.avif?t=1737034417\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293850/extras/1d6d06c9adf669985008213852a18310.webm?t=1737034417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293850/extras/1d6d06c9adf669985008213852a18310.mp4?t=1737034417\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基本操作</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用鼠标指向，用滚轮调节金箍棒基础长度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按住空格伸长金箍棒。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按C键大哭。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >背景故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >佛祖曰：那南赡部洲者，纵情声（Hifi）色（8K），多杀（狼人杀）多争（排位赛）。我今有低预算小游一款，画风丑陋，望之眼胀头痛；难度逆天，玩之脑门皆裂。今借贵地寻善信，能破此难关者，定是那西游取经人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发者的话</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款自我惩罚风格的游戏，灵感来自《Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy》、《Jump King》。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >众所周知，唐僧取经需要经历81难。除了本难关外，后续的80难会以DLC为载体发布，并通过不同的游戏形式呈现，希望有你喜欢的风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果觉得难度过低，请及时联系我。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >警告</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏不适合有癫痫、光敏、心脏病、高血压、脑血栓、精神类疾病等相关病史的玩家。</p>",
